{"tid":247982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"八婆袁彌明間生活百貨上市搞成點？","createTime":"2017-05-18T08:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T09:33:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe977f0e9620c7a9b045be820a0512f03c96027a","tid":247982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"無晒聲氣？ 過左上市聆訊未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170124/large/1485261580_6152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170124%2Flarge%2F1485261580_6152.jpg&h=762354cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170124/large/1485261389_83ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170124%2Flarge%2F1485261389_83ff.jpg&h=1f7cf162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年01月24日<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">袁彌明旗下「百貨店」謀創業板上市</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n已離開政界的前港姐袁彌明旗下「彌明生活百貨」剛遞交創業板上市申請，獨家保薦人為金利豐。該股現時於銅鑼灣、旺角、尖沙咀、沙田、荃灣、元朗共有6家零售店，出售護膚品、化妝品、食品及保健產品。<br />\n<br />\n袁彌明自任主席兼行政總裁，其夫林雨陽則任非執行董事。袁彌明胞姊袁彌望（43歲）則出任執董，與袁彌望同住的張肇漢（36歲）亦擔任非執董。招股書形容袁彌明為「傑出的社交媒體偶像」，林雨陽本身於2012至2016年期間，為網台Hong Kong New Media行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年9月底，該股半年收入4772萬元，亦為「Synergie Skin」、「pHion」等品牌的港澳地區獨家分銷商。<br />\n<br />\n集資所得將增設零售店、翻新現有零售店、在香港購置一個倉庫、擴大產品組合、增強網上營銷等。集團計劃於2019年3月底，在香港開設6家新零售店。"},{"pid":"865e89d8fd0edecc6ba20656db60291300fd0020","tid":247982,"uid":50872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac15d7108f61af2521385955b5db9c3450b1d88","tid":247982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"次次行過, 永遠唔見有客, 又竟然有收入<br />\n<br />\n認真神乎其技！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/APP/GEM/2017/2017012303/Documents/GEM201701240006_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2FAPP%2FGEM%2F2017%2F2017012303%2FDocuments%2FGEM201701240006_c.pdf&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=be2373ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/APP/GEM/2017/2017012303/Documents/GEM201701240006_c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"4a078f73197141ca4cb332df04feed1b4e2b6ae9","tid":247982,"uid":57166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"上到先算啦"},{"pid":"e8b58af56c3e53d11036405541820eb1166ea6d6","tid":247982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"林雨陽唔係食腦燒, 就係食老婆<br />\n<br />\n之前有班廢物話佢做教育搵到好多錢, <br />\n但永遠講唔出教乜春育<br />\n上市即刻無得講大話<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/v7jl36dgt/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Fv7jl36dgt%2Fimage.jpg&h=1318afce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c5fc9a20bbbd073f479619c00482d82891e6927","tid":247982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上到先算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKEX顯示處理中, 未退回"},{"pid":"9ff5491953cc093dda8f0e2ffc977dc68f4470e8","tid":247982,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林雨陽唔係食腦燒, 就係食老婆<br />\n<br />\n之前有班廢物話佢做教育搵到好多錢, <br />\n但永遠講唔出教乜春育<br />\n上市即刻無得講大話<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/v7jl36dgt/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postim